summary: This is a compatibility patch to make Cliffracers and Realistic Needs & Diseases (RND) compatible. It also makes the mod more lore friendly, as you won't see that many cliffracers as there are in the original mod. The 'Cliffracer Stew' is now less powerful.
descriptionHtml:
This is an Alpha version - Please test this mod and tell me if the Cliffracer Stew is balanced with the game. The Cliffracer stew values are adjusted for balance with SkyRe and RND. Please tell me if you think it is overpowered or underpowered.
